  <body>
    <p>A <term>schema annotation</term> is a documentation snippet associated with the definition of
      an element or attribute in a schema. If such a schema is associated with an XML document, the
      annotations are displayed in the <uicontrol>Content Completion Assistant</uicontrol>.</p>
